&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive legal strategy and maintain ownership of legal matters across all data center development phases, serving as the central legal point for the deal team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with internal stakeholders, including development, operations, asset management and strategic finance teams, to align legal strategies with the company’s business goals and project timelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft, review, and negotiate complex real estate agreements, including&amp;nbsp;purchase and sale agreements, leases, joint venture agreements, loan documents, construction contracts, purchase options, easements, and access agreements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise site diligence workstreams across title, survey, environmental, geotech, and zoning, coordinating directly with the development team and internal/external legal team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and support all legal matters related to project financing and debt raises.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide legal counsel across all phases of data center construction, including design, execution, construction, construction management and commissioning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft, review, and negotiate complex construction contracts including design build agreements and guaranteed maximum price contracts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage legal matters related to construction claims, liens, delays, defects, and site safety compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct outside counsel and manage project legal budgets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Invest in training, mentoring, and scaling of the legal counsel and paralegal support resources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT YOU&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a rigorous, detail-oriented approach to reviewing title, survey, environmental, and zoning reports for large-scale infrastructure or energy projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You excel at managing high-volume document workflows, tracking critical deadlines, and maintaining strict version control across multiple simultaneous site acquisitions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a strategic thinker with a practical, business-oriented approach to legal issues

