&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT HUT 8&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Imagine the ultimate destination for those who want to work at the cutting edge of technology, &lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;energy,&lt;/span&gt; and infrastructure. Hut&amp;nbsp;8 is on a mission to build and operate some of the world’s largest data centers for next-generation computing workloads, including AI, Colocation, Cloud, and Bitcoin Mining. We are proud to offer interesting and challenging opportunities for individuals who want to build teams, solve problems, and make an impact from day one. If you’re an ambitious individual looking for a career that is as rewarding as it is challenging, you’ve come to the right place.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the primary lead for our most complex agreements, you will personally negotiate the contracts that sit between our physical data center assets and our digital products. Your main goal is to act as an air traffic controller for our inventory, ensuring every megawatt we own is driving the highest possible return.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will define our off-take strategy by deciding whether to lease raw data center space to hyperscalers or run the capacity ourselves as cloud clusters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will lead negotiations for our largest contracts, managing the process from the initial term sheet through to the final legal redlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will balance physical inventory with digital demand to ensure we maximize utilization and eliminate unused capacity across our footprint.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will partner with finance and infrastructure teams to align our commercial deals with our actual power and site constraints.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT YOU&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are a commercial leader who understands the physical and financial sides of the data center industry. You know how to read a technical lease and how to pitch a high-value cloud service to a sophisticated buyer.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Experience:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a background in data center colocation or cloud infrastructure, specifically managing large-scale wholesale leases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have personally closed multi-million dollar deals and are comfortable sitting across the table from global tech leaders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You understand how to structure complex agreements that include tiered pricing, capacity reservations, and service level guarantees.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a strong communicator who can translate technical power and space requirements into clear business value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are excited to work in a fast-paced environment and help build a world-class commercial hub in Miami.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
