&lt;p&gt;Hut 8 develops and operates the infrastructure that powers next-generation technologies. Today, we are focused on developing data centers for AI. Across the industry, this infrastructure is built as undifferentiated, utilitarian buildings. We are creating a senior design role to redefine the form, function, and civic role of these facilities. The opportunity is to define the architecture of a new typology and the civic campus around it.&lt;br&gt;The role owns the architecture and design of everything we build: data centers, offices and workplaces, and the asset types to come. The first expression is the data center: a coherent architectural language that makes our infrastructure read as civic architecture rather than industrial backdrop on a campus that serves the public realm.&lt;br&gt;The role carries real authority and works within real constraints, directing leading architecture and design firms, engaging at the earliest stage of each project, and working alongside engineering and development as a peer. The mandate is to produce lasting architecture and genuinely civic sites within those constraints.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CORE RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define the architectural language of our infrastructure,&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;a coherent identity spanning building form, exterior expression, and interior environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define our campus model,&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;including the public, landscape, and amenity program of each site.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct top third-party architecture and design firms to develop and realize that vision,&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;holding them to the standard you set.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead internal and external project teams&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;to deliver large-format projects on schedule and on budget.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT YOU&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are a registered architect operating at the level of Design Director, Design Principal, or senior design lead on flagship projects at a top practice. The role requires the ability to establish a distinct architectural identity and the discipline to design within rigid, mission-critical constraints.&lt;/p&gt;
